		</p>
		<p>
			<a href="https://github.com/LenceOfTheOrder" class="btn btn-link my-2">My GitHub Profile</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/LenceOfTheOrder/cs-3300" class="btn btn-link my-2">Git Repo for this project</a>
